query:
SELECT
            c.name AS "name: KrateName",
            r.version AS "version: Version"
        FROM crates AS c
        JOIN releases AS r
            ON c.id = r.crate_id
        JOIN release_build_status AS rbs
            ON rbs.rid = r.id
        JOIN builds AS b
            ON b.rid = r.id
            AND b.build_finished = rbs.last_build_time
            AND b.rustc_nightly_date >= $1
            AND b.rustc_nightly_date < $2
